      "title": "A state of emergency is declared",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Acting President has declared a state of emergency effective from today.",
        "This state of emergency has been declared to provide essential services and provide public services to ensure public safety and the recovery of the country.",
        "On the order of Acting President Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe, President's Secretary Mr. Gamini Senarath has announced this state of emergency in a gazette notice."
      ],
